the trail's run out.

24:51.240 --> 24:52.617
We lost him.

24:53.742 --> 24:56.666
Okay, team.

24:56.829 --> 24:58.297
What now?

24:58.455 --> 24:59.627
JACKSON: Let's make camp.

24:59.790 --> 25:02.339
We can pick up the trail
when it gets light out.

25:07.006 --> 25:08.258
