JACKSON: Stop the truck.

27:30.065 --> 27:33.285
Right up there.
You see those trees with the rocks?

27:33.443 --> 27:35.662
The rocks along the base.

27:37.739 --> 27:40.834
Yes. Looks like their den.

27:43.829 --> 27:46.002
If we can isolate one
leopard, we may have a chance.

27:46.165 --> 27:47.291
What if we can't?

27:52.796 --> 27:54.423
You ready?

27:55.090 --> 27:56.808
After you.

28:05.726 --> 28:10.857
