JACKSON: Hey, what are you doing?
What are you doing?

35:40.513 --> 35:41.935
- No, no. Jamie!
- Hey!

35:42.098 --> 35:43.850
[JAMIE SCREAMING,
THEN MITCH GRUNTS]

35:55.320 --> 35:57.573
What do we do?

35:57.739 --> 35:58.991
I don't know yet.

35:59.157 --> 36:01.706
They're not taking
Jamie for ransom.

36:02.786 --> 36:03.958
No.

36:05.747 --> 36:09.627
JACKSON: If we get an opening,
you take out the driver, we'll get Jamie.

36:09.793 --> 36:12.467
We just need a diversion.

36:21.221 --> 36:22.814
[SNARLING, THEN ALL SCREAMING]

36:23.932 --> 36:25.855
[GUNFIRE AND ALL SHOUTING
IN FOREIGN LANGUAGE]

36:32.023 --> 36:33.900
- Jamie. Come on.
- Come on, come on.

36:38.947 --> 36:40.290
- Go! Come on!
- It worked.

36:53.878 --> 36:56.131
You lied to me.

36:56.923 --> 36:59.142
- I did not.
- I checked all the flights into India.

36:59.300 --> 37:01.018
Your friends were
not on any of them.

37:02.220 --> 37:04.723
They're fugitives,
they cannot travel commercial.

37:04.889 --> 37:06.482
We paid for passage
on a cargo plane.

37:06.641 --> 37:08.188
There were three
undocumented planes

37:08.351 --> 37:11.230
that landed in Rajasthan in the
last 24 hours, I checked them too.

37:12.772 --> 37:14.490
Perhaps they changed their plan.

37:14.649 --> 37:16.401
No, they're sticking
to their plan.

37:16.568 --> 37:18.161
It's just not the
one you told me.

37:19.654 --> 37:22.783
And now, your sister will
die because of a useless lie.

37:25.535 --> 37:28.835
You will not kill her.
You can't.

37:29.289 --> 37:32.839
Because if you do,
you will have no leverage with me.

37:33.001 --> 37:35.129
I'm never gonna tell you
what it is you need to know.

37:37.046 --> 37:39.014
You're right, of course.

37:40.008 --> 37:44.229
Take her left hand.
Use the dullest blade you have.

37:51.394 --> 37:52.566
I'll come back in 10 minutes.

37:52.729 --> 37:54.609
Perhaps you will have
changed your mind by then,

37:54.773 --> 37:57.697
before we move on to
Nathalie's right hand.

38:05.575 --> 38:07.095
That was great what
you did back there.

38:07.744 --> 38:09.621
- What?
- What you did with the cub.

38:09.788 --> 38:11.631
- What?
- Mitch stuck the cub with a needle.

38:11.790 --> 38:14.350
His pain sent a distress call.
It was just like the lions in L.A.

38:14.501 --> 38:15.941
They communicate
over long distances.

38:16.085 --> 38:20.386
- Oh, that was you!
- I just put their mutation to good use.

38:20.548 --> 38:22.892
This little guy saved our lives.

38:23.051 --> 38:25.395
We did it, raHki.

38:25.553 --> 38:28.523
Man, you saved my life. I think.

38:29.098 --> 38:30.315
"What" What happened?

