- It's okay.
- What happened?

38:32.811 --> 38:35.030
Oh, my God.
Jackson, you've been shot!

38:35.188 --> 38:37.065
- Let me see, let me see.
- I'm fine.

38:37.232 --> 38:38.575
All right, here.

38:38.733 --> 38:41.282
